---
import { ModelConfigurator } from "../components/ModelConfigurator";
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---
<SiteLayout active="models" title="模型配置" description="查看、比较和导出 SenFate 的公开模型参数。">
  <section class="model-hero">
    <div class="page-intro compact"><div><span class="kicker">MODEL CONFIGURATION</span><h1>参数不藏在<br />代码背后。</h1></div><p>选择预设并调整公开权重。保存后的配置会驱动下一次完整计算，服务器会验证参数边界，并把配置指纹写入结果证书。</p></div>
    <ModelConfigurator client:load />
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
